name: Anatomonster: Herzloser
description:
Herzloser, creature of love that's lost in it's own bubble

This is a collection of little creatures that were created in my head. All of this poor little babies seem to be dangerous, weird or ugly with an instant judgement, but if you look closely, with more time and effort to really understand and know this babies, lies fear underneath them, terrified of others. Imagine how it feels having constant pain and itch in the back of your head but you cant see nor understand where it comes from… that’s how my babies feels.

Please take good care of them and give them a better home to heal their traumas.
